    "body": "The package creation documentation for `CMakePackage`-s incorrectly shows `configure_args()`, when it should use `cmake_args()`.\r\n\r\nThe relevant code block appears in this section:\r\nhttps://spack.readthedocs.io/en/latest/packaging_guide.html#cmakepackage\r\n\r\nThis leads to `spack install` silently discarding all build options.\r\n",
